y Hunter (TV series)|City Hunter]]'' (2002)\n* ''[[Cutie Honey: The Live]]'' (2007\u20132008)\n* ''[[Death Note (2015 TV series)|Death Note]]'' (2015)\n* ''[[Eko Eko Azarak (manga)#Dramas|Eko Eko Azarak]]'' (1997)\n* ''[[Eko Eko Azarak (manga)#Dramas|Eko Eko Azarak -eye-]]'' (2004)\n* ''[[Gokusen#Drama|Gokusen]]'' (2002)\n* ''[[Great_Teacher_Onizuka#Live-action|Great Teacher Onizuka]]'' (1998\u20132014)\n* ''[[Hell Teacher Nube#Drama|Hell Teacher Nube]]'' (2014)\n* ''[[It Started with a Kiss (TV series)|It Started with a Kiss]]'' (2005\u20132006)\n* ''[[Kakegurui (2018 TV series)|Kakegurui]]'' (2018\u20132019)\n* ''[[Kikaider 01]]'' (1973\u20131974)\n* ''[[Lone Wolf and Cub#Television series|Lone Wolf and Cub]]'' (1973\u20131976)\n* ''[[Lone Wolf and Cub#Television series|Lone Wolf and Cub (Kozure Okami)]]'' (2002\u20132004)\n* ''[[Marmalade Boy#Live-action television series|Marmalade Boy]]'' (2001\u20132002)\n* ''[[Mighty Atom (1959 TV series)|Mighty Atom]]'' (1959\u20131960)\n* ''[[Mischievous Kiss: Love in Tokyo]]'' (2013)\n* ''[[Mob Psycho 100]]'' (2018)\n* ''[[MPD Psycho]]'' (Japan, 2000)\n* ''[[Playful Kiss]]'' (2010)\n* ''[[Ouran High School Host Club#Live-action TV series and film|Ouran High School Host Club]]'' (2011)\n* ''[[Sexy Voice and Robo#TV drama|Sexy Voice and Robo]]'' (2007)\n* ''[[Sukeban Deka#Television series|Sukeban Deka]]'' (1985\u20131987)\n* ''[[Ani_ni_Tsukeru_Kusuri_wa_Nai!#Live_Action|Take My Brother Away]]'' (2018)\n* ''[[They Kiss Again]]'' (2007\u20132008)\n* ''[[Blood Hound (manga)#TV Drama|Vampire Host]]'' (2004)\n* ''[[Wild 7#Live action|Wild 7]]'' (1972\u20131973)\n* ''[[You're Under Arrest (manga)#TV drama|You're Under Arrest]]'' (2002)\n* ''[[Zettai Kareshi (TV series)|Zetai Karesh]]'' (2008)\n\n===Animated===\n* ''[[7 Seeds#Anime|7 Seeds]]'' (2019)\n* ''[[After School Dice Club#Anime|After School Dice Club]]'' (2019\u2013present)\n* ''[[Akame ga Kill!#Anime|Akame ga Kill!]]'' (2014)\n* ''[[Android Kikaider: The Animation]]'' (200